folder: Willets Point Boulev & Union Street, Queens, NY
text:
Willets Point Boulevard, north from Union Street toward Parsons Boulevard, showing some old houses (right) and rows of new ones (center). The part of Willets Point Boulevard shown here is the former Whitestone Avenue, main north-south thoroughfare from Flushing to Whitestone.

April 13, 1927

P. L. Sperr
title: Queens: Willets Point Boulev - Union Street
